{"tid":2063073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋覺得紅官遍地（吳重儀），其實藍屍同樣鬧緊啲官話偏幫手足","createTime":"2020-06-13T15:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T15:45:36.000Z","uid":125079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c225a858d232b6058dbc522e760e61f88b9fe3d3","tid":2063073,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:10:50.000Z","msg":"最近番工，有個死藍屍廢中大大聲講，依啲官偏幫手足，全部輕判，又有612撐，捉多啲，忙死佢哋<br />\n<br />\n好耐之前搭過既一架的士，藍的士狗又係講埋同一樣野<br />\n<br />\n我哋知道九成九官都係紅，而偏偏班藍屍仲要覺得某啲係黃官，只要判手足唔夠重，就係狗官（藍屍叫開）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黨媒，民賤聯完全用緊我地先啱既野變成支持佢地既立場</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我諗大家都聽唔少，藍屍個腦永遠只係接受到黨媒比佢哋既資訊，完全唔理真實情況，所以易入耳，唔洗經大腦思考既，先係最洗到佢哋腦既說話<br />\n<br />\n根本九成九都紅底，一個法官中立公正，而班藍屍只會唔知足咁覺得佢哋黃<br />\n<br />\n只有郭偉健，吳重儀，彭寶琴，嚴舜儀佢哋依啲，先係藍屍眼中既好髮官<br />\n<br />\nDepartment of Juggle DOJ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZmEaB5p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZmEaB5p.png&h=ffe35d68&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TFZmJLr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTFZmJLr.png&h=19ab2ef3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZwOKGw9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZwOKGw9.png&h=df209ba5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pWHzjiT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpWHzjiT.png&h=7b3eaba9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3104163eb05821a67b3edb1b2e02569a8cda280","tid":2063073,"uid":334720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:18:16.000Z","msg":"屌到佢地兩面不是人"},{"pid":"ca2b45a91b65f9e79afe2696fa36cb5765cf6466","tid":2063073,"uid":54381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:18:47.000Z","msg":"因為佢地只係睇立場黎判斷所謂啱定錯, 佢地係唔會講道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48695fa94eaa0e979dec84525ee6d17bba9444e","tid":2063073,"uid":125079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca2b45a91b65f9e79afe2696fa36cb5765cf6466","tid":2063073,"uid":54381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:18:47.000Z","msg":"因為佢地只係睇立場黎判斷所謂啱定錯, 佢地係唔會講道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:30:39.000Z","msg":"對於一啲深層少少既野 佢哋個腦係唔想聽/抗拒接受<br />\n<br />\n唔想理解<br />\n<br />\n點解中共可以咁洗到佢哋腦？因為港共同保皇狗永遠講啲膚淺又簡單直接易明既說話<br />\n<br />\n令到佢哋覺得，係喎你講得冇錯，但完全冇考慮過背後同深層次既野"},{"pid":"17d1f3b3a1208cc1b55893182ec29c38c05aeceb","tid":2063073,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:36:57.000Z","msg":"大家可以睇睇依段片 ovmd 同民賤聯既訪問<br />\n<br />\n楊岳橋問既野張國鈞<del></del>永遠冇正面回應 每次都將法治同法律混淆<br />\n<br />\n因為保皇狗支持者眼中白紙黑字既法律就係一切<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">藍屍永遠只係睇到表面，法律<br />\n<br />\n深層既法治，唔想理唔想聽</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sB4qQwfS7Pw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsB4qQwfS7Pw&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=46f05e71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sB4qQwfS7Pw</a>"},{"pid":"09ee8d3668648d9dba90cf9925328aa45bb03b76","tid":2063073,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:44:53.000Z","msg":"班藍屍支那狗連林鄭都話係黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab3d4595b300f5f7ff1d5a94ecd7c030f0b2bc7","tid":2063073,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:45:36.000Z","msg":"香港表面好靚 但皮肉下既腐爛<br />\n<br />\n真係令人好痛心"}]}